{
  "texts": [
    "The mysterious language basically matches the tarot persona, but I also wanted the AI to be more human-like and less logical because humans are not always rational. \"",
    "Increasing emotional intensity and breaking neutrality.To elicit more vivid responses, many participants want the chatbot to also express emotions by exhibiting its own personality and opinions instead of maintaining an official, polite, and neutral role (P3, P4, P12, P18, P20).",
    "For example, P20 created a chatbot to play their roommate whom they had an argument with and specified that it should act \"particularly argumentative and disrespectful during their conversations. \"",
    "P3, while customizing the chatbot to be their crush, describe it as a person who has \"fewer polite expressions, more emotional expressions, less lecturing\" and even uses \"offensive expressions\" to authentically mimic their crush's bold and direct communication styles in real life.",
    "Similarly, P4 constructed a \"cyberpunk\" persona by explicitly telling the chatbot to \"use some profanity and actively vent with me. \""
  ]
}